{"tid":916794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【台灣地震】港有震感天文台接逾千報告 網民：震咗超過30秒","createTime":"2018-11-26T02:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T09:35:13.000Z","uid":40152,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ea76b6022d4c6950e9d3c5b5198fb12746abc4","tid":916794,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181126/_2018112609212975085.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181126%2F_2018112609212975085.jpg&h=09836860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣海峽發生地震，本港天文台表示，據初步分析，今早7時57分台灣海峽發生一次黎克特制5.9級地震，震中位於北緯23.36度，東經118.57度附近，即香港之東北偏東約470公里。有市民向天文台報告表示感到這次地震。<br />\n<br />\n天文台表示，接獲近千名市民報告指感到這次地震，震動維持數秒。初步分析顯示本港的地震烈度為修訂麥加利地震烈度表的第IV(四)度，即懸掛的物件擺動，門、窗、碗碟發出響聲。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民留言表示感到震感，「新蒲崗道感覺到，吊風扇冇開但輕微擺動」、「粉嶺都感覺到少少摇呀」、「深水埗區，今朝係床上面都感覺到，仲見部座地風扇有左右搖晃」、「九龍塘，震感，超過30秒」、「鑽石山被搖醒，震咗30秒」、「喺九龍城，度門都搖出聲」、「將軍澳也有，我坐在電腦枱前感到搖下搖下」，另外有不少網民指，初時以為自己頭暈，後來才得知發生地震。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1373025/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1373025%2F&d=azl4pq8h0FMwvaZgJeX2tsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=4024b1e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1373025%2F&h=b03658b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1373025/</a>"},{"pid":"86084a5e5a076c0ea16c460a570a8457316da264","tid":916794,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c1480e34138409e6a8194d825d37980c6c2ada","tid":916794,"uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":3,"s